d:Ge/Cylinder/RMin       = 0 cm
d:Ge/Cylinder/RMax       = 4 cm
d:Ge/Cylinder/HL 	     = 0.5 cm
d:Ge/Cylinder/TransX     = 0. m
d:Ge/Cylinder/TransY     = 0. m
d:Ge/Cylinder/TransZ     = 0. m
d:Ge/Cylinder/RotX       = 0. deg
